This simple Character Builder uses the Pickle DB files to create
a dynamic Character Builder:

$ Ghetto_Chara_Builder

      Classes              Key Ablities
------------------------------------------------------------
1   : Ardent               Charisma, Constitution, Wisdom
2   : Artificer            Intelligence, Constitution, Wisdom
3   : Assassin             Dexterity, Charisma, Constitution
4   : Avenger              Wisdom, Dexterity, Intelligence
5   : Barbarian            Strength, Constitution, Charisma
6   : Bard                 Charisma, Intelligence, Constitution
7   : Battlemind           Constitution, Wisdom, Charisma
8   : Cleric               Wisdom, Strength, Charisma
9   : Druid                Wisdom, Dexterity, Constitution
10  : Fighter              Strength, Dexterity, Wisdom, Constitution
11  : Invoker              Wisdom, Constitution, Intelligence
12  : Monk                 Dexterity, Strength, Wisdom
13  : Paladin              Strength, Charisma, Wisdom
14  : Psion                Intelligence, Charisma, Wisdom
15  : Ranger               Strength, Dexterity, Wisdom
16  : Rogue                Dexterity, Strength, Charisma
17  : Runepriest           Strength, Constitution, Wisdom
18  : Seeker               Wisdom, Strength, Dexterity
19  : Shaman               Wisdom, Constitution, Intelligence
20  : Sorcerer             Charisma, Dexterity, Strength
21  : Swordmage            Intelligence, Strength, Constitution
22  : Warden               Strength, Constitution, Wisdom
23  : Warlock              Charisma, Constitution, Intelligence
24  : Warlord              Strength, Intelligence, Charisma
25  : Wizard               Intelligence, Wisdom, Dexterity
------------------------------------------------------------


View Class: 

----

On each screen you are given a list of items, once you select
one of the items you get more detail:



Armor Proficiencies :
           Cloth, leather, hide
 
Bonus to Defense :
           +1 Reflex, +1 Will
 
Class Skills :
           Arcana (Int), Athletics (Str), Diplomacy (Cha),
           Endurance (Con), Heal (Wis), History (Int),
           Insight (Wis), Nature (Wis), Perception (Wis)
 
Healing Surges :
           7+ Constitution Modifier
 
Hit Points at 1st Level :
           12+ Constitution Score
 
Hit Points per Level Gained :
           5
 
Implements :
           Staff, Totem
 
Key Abilities :
           Wisdom, Dexterity, Constitution
 
Power Source :
           Primal. You have gained your powers through a
           careful study of and communion with the natural
           world.
 
Role :
           Controller. Your beast form gives you access to
           powers that provide control at close range, while
           your humanoid form allows you to hinder your
           opponents from a distance. Depending on your
           choice of class features and powers, you might
           lean toward either leader or striker as a
           secondary role.
 
Trained Skills :
           Nature. From the class skills list below, choose 3
           more trained skills at 1st level.
 
Weapon Proficiencies :
           Simple melee, simple ranged
 
Pick this Class (Y/n): 

